channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Virginia Tech Hokies Unveil New Football Uniforms Following Video Game Leak
item.description: Virginia Tech unveiled new uniforms on Thursday – one day earlier than expected – after having them leaked during a livestream of EA Sports' new College Football 25 video game.

item.title: L.A. Man Arrested For Animal Cruelty After Dropping Puppy Down Stairwell
item.description: A Los Angeles man is in custody after cops say he was caught on surveillance video dropping a 7-month-old puppy down an apartment staircase. The clip is horrifying, so watch at your own discretion -- in the video, a shirtless man cops identified as…

item.title: Purdue Boilermakers Reveal New Football Uniforms
item.description: Purdue unveiled new uniforms on Thursday that feature a striping pattern inspired by the Boilermakers' helmets under legendary coach Joe Tiller.

item.title: Brazilian Goalie Shot By Policeman's Rubber Bullet In Wild Post-Match Altercation
item.description: A post-match altercation between two soccer clubs in Brazil escalated so quickly -- a policeman actually fired a rubber bullet at a player's leg from point-blank range ... and the wild scene was all caught on video. It happened after a regional…

item.title: He’s Back! AHL’s Bridgeport Islanders Revive Fisherman For New Primary Logo
item.description: AHL affiliate of the New York Islanders borrow one of their parent club's most infamous logos and make a few changes to come up with their new look

item.title: Biden Supporters Watching Polls & Closing Checkbooks, Says Major Donor
item.description: President Biden's campaign funding might slow to a trickle if he stays in the race ... at least according to a 6-figure donor who says democratic supporters are analyzing poll numbers and reacting. Whitney Tilson's an author and investment expert…

item.title: Charly Launches New Kits for 5 Liga MX Clubs, Including Bespoke Shirts for Women’s Teams
item.description: Liga MX teams outfitted by sportswear brand include Club Santos Laguna, Club León, Atlas FC, CF Pachuca and Xolos de Tijuana

item.title: Travis Kelce, Christian McCaffrey Team Up For Commercial Shoot In L.A.

item.title: New Women’s 3-on-3 Basketball League Unveils Logo
item.description: Unrivaled league will feature six teams of five players each playing compressed full-court 3-on-3 games in Miami starting in January 2025
